Saving Throw: Special

This spell creates a severe blast of air that originates from the caster, affecting all enemies in its path. Those within 5 feet must make a save vs. breath or be blown back by the force of the gust and knocked unconscious for 1 round. In addition, this spell will disperse all clouds (including magically created vapors such as Cloudkill) as well as any insect swarms in the caster's current area.~

